data.description: Turn Key!!! Ready for you just in time to Decorate for all the Holidays. Lots of space for a growing family in this Beautiful Home & Well Established, Sought after Neighborhood. Dramatic 2 Story Foyer, Front & Rear Staircases, Open Family Room with Stone (gas) Fireplace, Eat in Kitchen with Granite Counters, Large Island, Recessed & Under Cabinet Lights. Formal Rooms, Dining Room with Tray Ceiling, Chair Rail & Crown Molding. Rec Room or Office Opens to Large Deck, Overlooking Giant, Fenced in Private Backyard. Spacious Primary Suite with Spa Like Bathroom, Garden Tub, Separate Shower & Huge Walk in Closet. Freshly refinished wood floors on first floor, Brand new carpet throughout entire home. Exterior is Freshly Power Washed Vinyl Siding & Deck Stained. Large 2 Car Garage, Front & Side Irrigated Yard. Brand new roof 2020, Fence 2023, Newer HVAC. Sidewalks/Bike Paths, Tennis Courts, Community Pool with Lots of Events. 2 Elementary Schools Just Minutes Down the Road & Walking Distance to Cosby High School. Conveniently located near Rt288 & Powhite Parkway. Minutes From Shopping & Great Restaurants.
